definitions.definition: Physical exercises with the participation of a multitude of muscles and often minimal equipment (thus, usually bodyweight exercises ); strength training aspects and cardio aspects are both involved, and stamina is often a focus.

main_definition: ( in the plural ) Physical exercises with the participation of a multitude of muscles and often minimal equipment (thus, usually bodyweight exercises ); strength training aspects and cardio aspects are both involved, and stamina is often a focus.
secondary_definitions: ( in the singular ) A system of such exercises.
